rComments: I took DTSB01 and DTSB02. This professor is both kind and helpful. The class material is very interesting and so are his lectures. He talks pretty fast and he doesn't use slides so taking notes can be a struggle but are necessary. There is a lot of material to cover in the course. Also he responds to emails very quickly! which is always  a plus.

Very intellectual. Awesome prof, I thoroughly enjoyed his class. His lectures are very interesting and his in class examples are very useful and relevant. Also, I found him to be one of the most helpful prof I have ever had, he is good with emails and is always ready to clarify your understanding.
POLA81.One of the best profs ever. Makes the class interesting and does NOT read from slides, which I think is awesome. His lectures never make me sleepy.

Took DTSB01 and DTSB02. Very good prof. Can get a little bit confusing at times, but have had some very good class discussions. The paper can be hard if you're not following in class. Attendance = Easy 10%. I'd recommend this class to anyone!
